high_descs: go the nightstand next to the bed
pick up the pencil from the stand
take the pencil to the other nightstand with the lamp
turn the lamp on while holding the pencil
anns.task_desc: get the pencil and look at it under the lamp

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room.
Pick up the pen from the bedside table.
Turn around and walk to the end of the bed, then turn left and walk to the end of the bed, then turn left and walk across the room.
Turn on the lamp that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: To look at the pen in the light.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the wall and walk to the small wooden side table ahead.
Pick up the yellow pen behind the clock on top of the side table.
Turn around, hang a left at the end of the window and turn left at the far edge of the bed to reach the wooden side table with the small lamp.
Turn on the small lamp on the middle of the table.
anns.task_desc: Examine a pen by the light of a small lamp.
